                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Berlin"
                    },
                    "body": "Given that snappy has a very slow release cadence and the patch has been untouched for month now, would it maybe make sense to rely on a fork with the patch merged (e.g. Antoine's)?\r\n\r\nOpinions [~apitrou] [~kou] ?",
